  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">DTBK Tier II Inc</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Project is expected to have a high development impact in the following measurable areas:  1-Increasing credit availability to the SMEs and Very Small Enterprises (VSEs);  2- Supporting job creation by financing the SME and VSEs. The VSEs are a high impact sector, which has low access to finance. Financing this sub-segment helps create opportunities to achieving more balanced growth; 3. Capacity building to help the bank to service VSEs on a sustainable basis; and   4. Demonstration effect/market transformation through DTBK&apos;&apos;s continued lending to the target segment beyond the life of the Project.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The proposed project entails an IFC investment of $20 million, in the form of a subordinated loan that qualifies as Tier II Capital, to be extended to Diamond Trust Bank Limited (DTBK). The above facility will be utilized to: (i) strengthen the banks capital base; and (ii) help the bank to expand its lending activities to SMEs.</narrative>
  </description>
